{"id":916,"parent_id":909,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":916,"title":"Amos 7","subtitle":"","short_title":"Amos","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 7"],[".studySummary",["i","Amos relates how he was called of God to be a prophet—He prophesies the captivity of Israel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.1","order":"02.31.007.61415"},["b","1"],"Thus hath the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"shewed unto me; and, behold, he formed grasshoppers in the beginning of the shooting up of the latter growth; and, lo,",["i","it was"],"the latter growth after the king’s mowings."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.2","order":"02.31.007.61416"},["b","2"],"And it came to pass,",["i","that"],"when they had made an end of eating the grass of the land, then I said, O Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", forgive, I beseech thee: by whom shall Jacob arise? for he",["i","is"],"small."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.3","order":"02.31.007.61417"},["b","3"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"The"],["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"repented"],"for this: It shall not be, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.4","order":"02.31.007.61418"},["b","4"],"¶Thus hath the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"shewed unto me: and, behold, the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"called to contend by fire, and it devoured the great deep, and did eat up a part."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.5","order":"02.31.007.61419"},["b","5"],"Then said I, O Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", cease, I beseech thee: by whom shall Jacob arise? for he",["i","is"],"small."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.6","order":"02.31.007.61420"},["b","6"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"The"],["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"repented for this: This also shall not be, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.7","order":"02.31.007.61421"},["b","7"],"¶Thus he shewed me: and, behold, the Lord stood upon a wall",["i","made"],"by a plumbline, with a plumbline in his hand."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.8","order":"02.31.007.61422"},["b","8"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto me, Amos, what seest thou? And I said, A plumbline. Then said the Lord, Behold, I will set a plumbline in the midst of my people Israel: I will not again",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"pass"],"by them any more:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.9","order":"02.31.007.61423"},["b","9"],"And the high places of Isaac shall be desolate, and the sanctuaries of Israel shall be laid waste; and I will rise against the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"house"],"of Jeroboam with the sword."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.10","order":"02.31.007.61424"},["b","10"],"¶Then Amaziah the priest of Beth-el sent to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Jeroboam"],"king of Israel, saying, Amos hath conspired against thee in the midst of the house of Israel: the land is not able to bear all his words."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.11","order":"02.31.007.61425"},["b","11"],"For thus Amos saith, Jeroboam shall die by the sword, and Israel shall surely be led away captive out of their own land."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.12","order":"02.31.007.61426"},["b","12"],"Also Amaziah said unto Amos, O thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"seer"],", go, flee thee away into the land of Judah, and there eat bread, and prophesy there:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.13","order":"02.31.007.61427"},["b","13"],"But prophesy not again any more at Beth-el: for it",["i","is"],"the king’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"chapel"],", and it",["i","is"],"the king’s court."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.14","order":"02.31.007.61428"},["b","14"],"¶Then answered Amos, and said to Amaziah, I",["i","was"],"no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"prophet"],", neither",["i","was"],"I a prophet’s son; but I",["i","was"],"an herdman, and a gatherer of sycomore fruit:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.15","order":"02.31.007.61429"},["b","15"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"took me as I followed the flock, and the",["span.smallCaps",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Lord"]],"said unto me,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"Go"],",",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"prophesy"],"unto my people Israel."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.16","order":"02.31.007.61430"},["b","16"],"¶Now therefore hear thou the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": Thou sayest, Prophesy not against Israel, and drop not",["i","thy word"],"against the house of Isaac."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.17","order":"02.31.007.61431"},["b","17"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Thy wife shall be an harlot in the city, and thy sons and thy daughters shall fall by the sword, and thy land shall be divided by line; and thou shalt die in a polluted land: and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Israel"],"shall surely go into captivity forth of his land."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.3a","order":"02.31.007.61432"},["b","3a"],["span.small","JST"],"Amos 7:3",["i","And"],"the Lord",["i","said, concerning Jacob, Jacob shall repent"],"for this,",["i","therefore I will not utterly destroy him,"],"saith the Lord."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.3b","order":"02.31.007.61434"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/6.6"},"Gen. 6:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/23.19"},"Num. 23:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.6a","order":"02.31.007.61436"},["b","6a"],["span.small","JST"],"Amos 7:6",["i","And"],"the Lord",["i","said, concerning Jacob, Jacob shall repent of his wickedness; therefore I will not utterly destroy him,"],"saith the Lord God."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.8a","order":"02.31.007.61438"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/8.2"},"Amos 8:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.9a","order":"02.31.007.61440"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/15.10.8-12"},"2 Kgs. 15:10 (8–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.10a","order":"02.31.007.61442"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.1"},"Amos 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.12a","order":"02.31.007.61444"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seer"},"TG Seer"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.13a","order":"02.31.007.61446"},["b","13a"],["span.small","OR"],"sanctuary."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.14a","order":"02.31.007.61448"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.23.22-23"},"JS—H 1:23 (22–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.15a","order":"02.31.007.61450"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/called-of-god"},"TG Called of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.15b","order":"02.31.007.61452"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-keys-of"},"TG Priesthood, Keys of"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.15c","order":"02.31.007.61454"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophecy"},"TG Prophecy"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"Prophets, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.17a","order":"02.31.007.61456"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-ten-lost-tribes-of"},"TG Israel, Ten Lost Tribes of"],"."]]}
